title: VMware vCenter Server Appliance: Update Status
agents: vcsa_health
catalog: app/vmware
license: GPL-2.0-only
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the update status of a VMware vCenter Server
 Appliance (VCSA) and reports the installed product version. The data
 is retrieved by the special agent {agent_vcsa_health} from the
 appliance REST API.

 The state is {OK} if the appliance is up to date, {WARN} if updates
 are pending or an update is being staged or installed, and {CRIT} if
 an installation failed or a rollback is in progress.

discovery:
 One service is created per appliance.
